<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٠٠٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/634">إِسْمَاعِيلُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1760">خَالِدٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3667">أَبِي قِلَابَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كَانَ الْقُنُوتُ فِي الْمَغْرِبِ وَالْفَجْرِ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>